      static ClassDefinition SemanticUtils.resolveBaseClass(ICommonClassNode classNode, ClassDefinition classDefinition, ICompilerProject project, Collection<ICompilerProblem> problems)
      This is similar to the resolveBaseClass() method of IClassDefinition, except it reports problems if the base class doesn't exist, if it isn't actually a class, or if it is final; it also returns the class definition for Object in these error cases.
